The All-New AirPort Extreme Base Station Model ME918LLA
The all-new AirPort Extreme Base Station offers Wi-Fi speeds up to 3x faster than the previous generation. It features next-generation 802.11ac Wi-Fi a powerful beamforming antenna array for higher performance and range simultaneous dual-band support and a new vertical design with a smaller footprint. And AirPort Extreme is easy to set up and highly secure letting you share your broadband Internet connection a USB printer or a hard drive.
Key Features:
• Next-generation 802.11ac Wi-Fi for up to 3x faster data rates
• Powerful beamforming antenna array for higher performance and range
• All-new design with a smaller footprint
• Simultaneous dual-band Wi-Fi
• Easy setup with a Mac iPad iPhone or iPod touch
• Connect a USB printer or hard drive and access it wirelessly
• Secure connections and compatibility with Mac computers PCs iPhone iPad iPod touch Apple TV and more
